<meta property="og:title" content="A legacy from the 1800s leaves Tokyo facing blackouts" />
<meta property="og:url" content="http://www.itworld.com/business/140626/legacy-1800s-leaves-tokyo-facing-blackouts" />
<meta property="og:description" content="East Japan entered its fifth day of power rationing on Friday, with no end to the planned blackouts in sight. The power shortages began last week when a massive earthquake and tsunami knocked nuclear power stations offline. The local electrical utility can't make up the shortfall by importing power from another region, though, because Japan lacks a national power grid, a consequence of a decision taken in the late 1800s." />
